<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>HRUM - Cerita Saham Metode Kang Yayan</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg:     #05080f;
    --card:   #080e1a;
    --border: #0d1f38;
    --accent: #0ea5e9;
    --gold:   #f59e0b;
    --green:  #10b981;
    --red:    #ef4444;
    --purple: #8b5cf6;
    --text:   #cbd5e1;
    --muted:  #475569;
    --dim:    #1e293b;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #020917 0%, #0a1628 60%, #060d1c 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 18px 20px 14px;
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
  }
  .header-label {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--muted);
    font-family: monospace; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .header-row {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;
  }
  .ticker-name {
    font-size: 36px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }
  .ticker-price { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--red); }
  .ticker-chg   { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--red); }
  .ticker-sub   { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }
  .pills { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .pill {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;
  }
  .pill-l { font-size: 8px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .pill-v { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); }

  /* PAGE DOTS */
  .dot-nav {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 6px;
    padding: 12px 0 0;
  }
  .dot {
    height: 8px; border-radius: 4px; border: none;
    cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; background: var(--dim);
    width: 8px;
  }
  .dot.active { width: 24px; background: var(--accent); }
  .page-label {
    text-align: center; font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* CONTENT */
  .content {
    padding: 16px 16px 80px;
    max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .page { display: none; }
  .page.active { display: block; }

  /* CARDS */
  .card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .card-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--card), #0a1628);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .card-accent-left {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .divider {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    margin: 20px 0 14px;
  }
  .divider-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }
  .divider-text {
    font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 3px; font-family: monospace; white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* QUOTE */
  .quote {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1628, #0d1e35);
    border: 1px solid rgba(14,165,233,.2);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; margin: 12px 0;
  }
  .quote-text {
    font-size: 13px; color: #93c5fd; font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.7; font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }
  .quote-author { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 6px; }

  /* STATS GRID */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .stat-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; text-align: center;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }
  .stat-label { font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .stat-value { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 900; }
  .stat-sub   { font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 3px; }

  /* LOHAN GRID */
  .lohan-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .lohan-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 12px;
    border-top: 2px solid;
  }
  .lohan-title { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .lohan-desc  { font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* WYCKOFF */
  .wyckoff-badges {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center;
    justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .wyckoff-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
  .phase-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 900;
    background: transparent; border: 2px solid var(--dim); color: var(--dim);
  }
  .phase-badge.active {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; font-size: 11px; color: #000;
  }
  .phase-label { font-size: 7px; color: var(--muted); text-align: center; max-width: 40px; }
  .wyckoff-note {
    background: #0a1628; border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .wyckoff-note-title { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .wyckoff-note-desc  { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 3px; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* TIMELINE */
  .timeline-item { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 0; }
  .tl-line {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; min-width: 20px;
  }
  .tl-dot {
    width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--dim); border: 2px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 8px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .tl-dot.current { color: #000; }
  .tl-connector { width: 1px; flex: 1; background: var(--border); min-height: 20px; }
  .tl-body { padding-bottom: 18px; flex: 1; }
  .tl-head { display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .tl-emoji { font-size: 14px; }
  .tl-period { font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .tl-title  { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; }
  .tl-sub    { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .tl-desc   { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.8; margin-left: 22px; }

  /* SMELTER */
  .smelter-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    border-left: 4px solid;
  }
  .smelter-code  { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; }
  .smelter-name  { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text); }
  .smelter-own   { font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); }
  .smelter-asset { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; }
  .smelter-loc   { font-size: 8px; color: var(--muted); }

  /* REV BARS */
  .rev-row { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .rev-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .rev-seg  { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text); }
  .rev-chg  { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; }
  .rev-bar-row { display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; }
  .rev-old  { font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); min-width: 65px; text-align: right; }
  .rev-new  { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; min-width: 65px; }
  .rev-bar-wrap { flex: 1; background: var(--dim); border-radius: 3px; height: 8px; }
  .rev-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; }

  /* BANDARMOLOGY */
  .bando-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1022, #0d1628);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .bando-step { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .bando-num {
    width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold); display: flex; align-items: center;
    justify-content: center; color: #000; font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .bando-q { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .bando-a { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text); margin-top: 2px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* BROKER FLOW */
  .broker-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 7px;
  }
  .broker-name { font-weight: 800; min-width: 24px; font-size: 11px; }
  .broker-side {
    font-size: 9px; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 3px;
    font-weight: 700; min-width: 32px; text-align: center;
  }
  .broker-bar-wrap {
    flex: 1; background: var(--dim); border-radius: 3px;
    height: 10px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .broker-bar-fill { position: absolute; height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; }
  .broker-center { position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 0; width: 1px; height: 100%; background: var(--border); }
  .broker-net  { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; min-width: 38px; text-align: right; }
  .broker-note { font-size: 8px; color: var(--muted); flex: 1; }

  /* BUYBACK */
  .buyback-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #071020, #0a1628);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .insight-row {
    background: var(--card); border-left: 3px solid;
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px 12px; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .insight-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; }
  .insight-txt { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); }

  /* SCORECARD */
  .score-total {
    background: var(--card); border: 2px solid #f97316;
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .score-lbl  { font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .score-num  { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 900; color: #f97316; }
  .score-sub  { font-size: 20px; color: var(--muted); }
  .score-pct  { font-size: 11px; color: #f97316; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .score-bar-wrap { background: var(--dim); border-radius: 6px; height: 8px; }
  .score-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 6px; background: #f97316; }
  .score-note { font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 6px; }

  .scorebar { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .scorebar-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .scorebar-lbl  { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
  .scorebar-val  { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 900; }
  .scorebar-wrap { background: var(--dim); border-radius: 4px; height: 6px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .scorebar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; }
  .scorebar-desc { font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* RISK */
  .risk-item {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid; padding: 10px 12px; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .risk-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .risk-desc  { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* TRADE PLAN */
  .trade-row {
    display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 9px 12px; background: var(--card);
    border-left: 3px solid; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .trade-label { min-width: 115px; font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); }
  .trade-value { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 900; }
  .trade-note  { font-size: 9px; color: var(--dim); margin-top: 2px; }

  /* ENDING */
  .ending-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #050d1a, #0a1628);
    border: 1px solid rgba(14,165,233,.2);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px;
  }
  .ending-title {
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: #e2e8f0;
    line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }
  .ending-body {
    font-size: 10px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .ending-decision {
    background: #050e1a; border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px; border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .ending-dec-title { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .ending-dec-body  { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer-txt {
    text-align: center; font-size: 9px; color: var(--dim);
    padding: 16px 0 0; line-height: 2;
  }

  /* NAV */
  .nav-bar {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    margin-top: 24px; padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .nav-btn {
    padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.3; cursor: not-allowed; }
  .nav-prev { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); color: var(--muted); }
  .nav-next { border: 1px solid var(--accent); background: var(--card); color: var(--accent); }
  .nav-lbl  { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); text-align: center; max-width: 140px; }

  /* UTILS */
  .flex-base { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 12px; }
  .section-title { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 700; }
  .mt8  { margin-top: 8px; }
  .mt12 { margin-top: 12px; }
  .mb12 { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  strong { font-weight: 700; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="header">
  <div class="header-label">IDX : HRUM &nbsp; CERITA SAHAM &nbsp; METODE KANG YAYAN</div>
  <div class="header-row">
    <div>
      <div class="flex-base">
        <span class="ticker-name">HRUM</span>
        <span class="ticker-price">Rp 995</span>
        <span class="ticker-chg">-1.49%</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ticker-sub">PT Harum Energy Tbk &middot; Batu Bara + Nickel HPAL &middot; IDX</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pills">
      <div class="pill"><div class="pill-l">MKT CAP</div><div class="pill-v">Rp 13.5T</div></div>
      <div class="pill"><div class="pill-l">52W RANGE</div><div class="pill-v">760-1.305</div></div>
      <div class="pill"><div class="pill-l">LABA 1Q26</div><div class="pill-v">+272% YoY</div></div>
      <div class="pill"><div class="pill-l">FASE</div><div class="pill-v">Phase B/C</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- DOT NAV -->
<div class="dot-nav">
  <button class="dot active" onclick="goPage(1)" id="dot1"></button>
  <button class="dot" onclick="goPage(2)" id="dot2"></button>
  <button class="dot" onclick="goPage(3)" id="dot3"></button>
  <button class="dot" onclick="goPage(4)" id="dot4"></button>
</div>
<div class="page-label" id="pageLabel">Halaman 1 / 4</div>

<div class="content">

  <!-- ===== PAGE 1: CERITA & TIMELINE ===== -->
  <div class="page active" id="page1">

    <div class="card-gradient">
      <div class="section-title" style="color:var(--accent)">CERITA SAHAM INI</div>
      <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:900;color:#e2e8f0;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:8px;font-family:Georgia,serif">
        Dari Raja Batu Bara ke Tuan Nikel
        <span style="color:var(--gold)"> &mdash; Transformasi yang Belum Selesai</span>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8">
        Tipe: <strong style="color:var(--gold)">Transformasi Bisnis</strong> &mdash;
        Konglomerat batu bara yang bertaruh besar pada nikel.
        Dari puncak Rp 2.400 ke lembah Rp 760, lalu kini berdiri di Rp 995.
        Apakah ini dasar dari babak baru, atau sekadar istirahat sebelum turun lagi?
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="quote">
      <div class="quote-text">&ldquo;HRUM bukan lagi perusahaan batu bara. Ia sedang menjadi raksasa nikel. Tapi proses transformasi selalu menyakitkan &mdash; dan inilah harganya.&rdquo;</div>
      <div class="quote-author">&mdash; Analisa Metode Kang Yayan</div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"><div class="divider-line"></div><div class="divider-text">TEORI IKAN LOHAN &mdash; HRUM EDITION</div><div class="divider-line"></div></div>

    <div class="lohan-grid">
      <div class="lohan-card" style="border-color:var(--green)">
        <div class="lohan-title" style="color:var(--green)">FASE 1&#10;Akumulasi</div>
        <div class="lohan-desc">2020-2022: HRUM bangun kerajaan nikel diam-diam. Investasi besar di HPAL Halmahera. Retail tidak tahu.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lohan-card" style="border-color:var(--gold)">
        <div class="lohan-title" style="color:var(--gold)">FASE 2&#10;PomPom</div>
        <div class="lohan-desc">2022: Harga batu bara ATH, HRUM naik ke Rp 2.400. Semua orang tahu. Nikel jadi narasi tambahan.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lohan-card" style="border-color:var(--red)">
        <div class="lohan-title" style="color:var(--red)">FASE 3&#10;Menggoreng</div>
        <div class="lohan-desc">2022-2023: Distribusi besar dari puncak. Harga turun tajam ke Rp 760. Retail tertinggal di atas.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lohan-card" style="border-color:#f97316">
        <div class="lohan-title" style="color:#f97316">FASE 4&#10;Cuci Piring</div>
        <div class="lohan-desc">2023-2026: Panjang dan menyakitkan. Harga turun 2.400 ke 760. Foreign jual terus. Kita di sini.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:14px">
      <div class="section-title" style="color:var(--accent)">POSISI WYCKOFF SEKARANG</div>
      <div class="wyckoff-badges">
        <div class="wyckoff-item">
          <div class="phase-badge" style="border-color:var(--red);color:var(--red)">A</div>
          <div class="phase-label">Distribusi</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wyckoff-item">
          <div class="phase-badge active" style="background:#f97316;box-shadow:0 0 12px #f9731666">B</div>
          <div class="phase-label" style="color:var(--gold)">Akumulasi</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wyckoff-item">
          <div class="phase-badge" style="border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold)">C</div>
          <div class="phase-label">Spring</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wyckoff-item">
          <div class="phase-badge" style="border-color:var(--green);color:var(--green)">D</div>
          <div class="phase-label">Markup</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wyckoff-item">
          <div class="phase-badge" style="border-color:var(--purple);color:var(--purple)">E</div>
          <div class="phase-label">Breakout</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wyckoff-note">
        <div class="wyckoff-note-title">Kita ada di Phase B menuju C</div>
        <div class="wyckoff-note-desc">Distribusi dari Rp 2.400 sudah selesai. Harga sedang proses akumulasi diam-diam. Tunggu konfirmasi Spring di area 950-975 sebelum aman masuk.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"><div class="divider-line"></div><div class="divider-text">PERJALANAN HRUM</div><div class="divider-line"></div></div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="tl-line">
        <div class="tl-dot" style="border-color:var(--red);background:var(--red);color:#000"></div>
        <div class="tl-connector"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-body">
        <div class="tl-head"><span class="tl-emoji">&#128293;</span><div><div class="tl-period">2021-2022 | PHASE A</div><div class="tl-title" style="color:var(--red)">Era Kejayaan Batu Bara</div><div class="tl-sub">ATH Rp 2.400</div></div></div>
        <div class="tl-desc">Harga batu bara global meroket akibat krisis energi. HRUM menangguk untung besar, revenue melebihi USD 400 juta per kuartal. Di balik layar, manajemen sudah membangun fondasi bisnis baru: nickel smelter di Halmahera.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="tl-line">
        <div class="tl-dot" style="border-color:#f97316;background:#f97316;color:#000"></div>
        <div class="tl-connector"></div>
      </div>
